\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\hat{A}=\int_{a_{\text{min}}}^{a_{\text{max}}}daa\left|a\right\rangle \left\langle a\right|.
\]

\end_inset

This theory has the following postulates: 
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

